_sText:
zm_unv_world_v2 is warehouse-themed map. 

Since the old version of the map isn't good, i decided to make the 2nd version of the map. This version of the map provides improvement of the 1st version of the map.

It has 64 player spawns, some spots to barricade, or to hold.

Things that have been modified (comparing v1 to v2):
  • Some barricading/holding spot still remains in this map, but the rest are removed.
  • The map is now larger than the 1st version, and contains more spots.
  • The original version did not have any secrets, but there are a few secrets in this version.


The original map thread:
http://plaguefest.com/threads/zm_unv_world.20462/

If there are bugs in the map, please notify me and i'll try to fix it.
